name: Ravnika ( sprawling fantasy city )
description:
Make a sprawling high fantasy gothic city of your dream true !
Works well as a background !


This is a Lora I made to celebrate me finally making kohya_ss work on my jank !

Trained on ProtogenAnime, works on other models fine.
Do tend to go towards discoloration, prompt it out.
A review would be cool to have !

Here is my ko-fi if you want to donate: https://ko-fi.com/maidragora
